## üé® COLOR & VISUAL IDENTITY (FULL FREEDOM)

Forget traditional corporate blue.

Design a **high-energy, modern electric palette**, for example:

* Dark, near-black base (graphite / obsidian)
* Electric cyan / plasma blue
