## üì¶ LIBRARIES YOU MAY USE (IF HELPFUL)

You may introduce:

* Framer Motion
* Lenis / smooth scrolling (if SEO-safe)
* Tailwind CSS (preferred)
* CSS variables for theming
* Lightweight SVG or WebGL effects

Do NOT:

* Break SSR
* Hide content from crawlers
* Inject text via canvas only

